quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,38,"Duca tuvuga duti:- nimumanuke mwese kw’Isi, nimwashikirwa n’uburongozi buvuye iwanje, n’abazo kurikira uburongozi bwanje ntabwoba buzoba buri kuribo kandi ntibazo teterwa"
  2,39,"Mugabo abazo hakana n’ukutemera aya majambo yacu, abo nibo bazoba bari mu bantu bo mu muriro udahera, muriwo niho hazoba hari ubwicaro bwabo bwamisi yose"
  2,40,"Mwebwe ruvyaro rwa bene israeri, nimwibuke imigisha yanje nabahezagiye kuriyo, kandi mukurikire amasezerano yanje, nanje nzokurikiza amasezerano yanyu, kandi muntinye jewe gusa"
  2,41,"Kandi mwemere ivyo namanuye vyemeza mubiri kumwe namwe, mugabo ntimube mubambere muguhakana, kandi ntimugurishe aya amajambo yanje kukiguzi gitoyi, kandi muntinye jewe gusa"
  2,42,"Kandi ntimuvange ukuri hamwe n’ibinyoma, hanyuma mugaca munyegeza uko kuri mugihe mukuzi"
  2,43,"Nimuhagarike amasengesho, kandi mutange n’imperezwa, kandi mwuname hamwe n’abunama"
  2,44,"Mbega mutegeka abantu kugira ineza, hanyuma mukibagiza imitima yanyu mugihe musoma igitabu c’Imana none mwebwe ntimutegera"
  2,45,"Nimwihangane kandi mwigumye hamwe n’ugusenga, kuko mu vy’ukuri ico kintu kiragoye cane, dukuyemwo abantu b’abagamburutsi nyakuri"
  2,46,Nabafise ivyemezo vy’ukuri yuko bazohura n’Umuremyi wabo kandi bazosubizwa iwe
  2,47,"Mwebwe ruvyaro rwa bene israeri, nimwibuke imigisha yanje nabahaye hamwe n’iteka nabateye gusumba ibindi biremwa vyose"
  2,48,"Kandi mutinye wamusi umutima w’umuntu ataco uzofasha uwundi mutima kukintu icarico cose, kandi ntihazo kwemerwa ibisabisho vyanyu, kandi ntihazo kwakirwa icoba kombora kivuye kuriwe, kandi ntibazoronka ikizoba kingira"